      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation scenario demonstrated to be sufficiently representative of the intended use scenario.",
      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 test configuration is the FDA-recognized standard for spinal construct mechanical performance; geometry, loading, and boundary conditions replicate the regulatory submission scenario; multi-laboratory execution increases confidence in result generalizability."
