    "rationale": "Overall credibility is sufficient for regulatory submission. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted based on regulatory precedent for single-condition ASTM F1717 testing and the absence of evidence that multi-condition testing would alter the submission decision.",
